My throat is hoarse. What are you doing here?

64
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:52,500
- I didn't hear you. 
 - Why are you spacing out?

65
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:55,000
Are you done? Let's get off work.

66
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:58,700
What do you mean? Did you come to work these days?

67
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:02,500
You either sleep here or just space out. You leave before 7 p.m. every day. What are you up to?

68
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:06,100
- I have things to do. 
 - What's going on? Which girl has deceived you?

69
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:08,500
Cheated out of money or heartbroken?

70
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:12,500
Are you serious? Why would you wish that for me?

71
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,300
- Do I look like a fool that everyone can deceive? 
 - You are a fool.

72
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:20,900
- You've been deceived several times. I had no control over you before. 
 - You don't have any control over me now.

73
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:26,300
Now we're roommates running a business together. I have a duty to manage your money.

74
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:28,100
- On what grounds? 
 - On what grounds?

75
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:30,300
Why should you manage my money?

76
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:32,800
You can provide for me, and I'll give all my money to you.

77
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,500
Fine, I'll provide for you. Give it all to me.

78
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:39,500
- I'll pay you monthly, so that you can't be cheated out of money. 
 - He Xindi.

79
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:43,600
That's enough. You...

80
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,900
You want to monopolize me.

81
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:49,000
You like me, right?

82
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:52,300
- If you like me, just say so. I could consider it. 
 - Get over yourself.

83
00:07:52,300 --> 00:07:56,200
But let me be clear first. I'm not seeking marriage now.

84
00:07:58,500 --> 00:08:00,100
Despicable.

85
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:03,500
- What are you doing? 
 - Leave me alone.

86
